description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a dynamic and forward thinking, physiotherapist to join our established therapy team at Hawkhurst Community Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The multidisciplinary team work together to provide evidence based, patient centred rehabilitation plans to patients with a variety of physical and medical problems who require an inpatient stay prior to safe return home.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interviews will be held on 16th November 2020. You will also receive a call after the advert closes to have a chat about your aspirations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome applications from all groups in the community and will accommodate needs and make adjustments wherever possible. We welcome applications from individuals from diverse backgrounds and those covered by the Equalities Act.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Rachel Ellis&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 0300 123 4081 / 07747 513397&lt;/p&gt;
